2 October\n| [[Ninian Park]], [[Cardiff]]\n| {{fb|Wales}}\n| align=center|0\u20130\n| [[1965\u201366 British Home Championship]]\n| \n|-\n| align=center|47\n| 20 October\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|Austria}}\n| align=center|2\u20133\n| Friendly\n| \n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''1966'''\n|-\n| align=center|48\n| 4 May\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|Yugoslavia}}\n| align=center|2\u20130\n| Friendly\n| 1\n|-\n| align=center|49\n| 29 June\n| [[Ullevaal Stadion]], Oslo\n| {{fb|Norway}}\n| align=center|6\u20131\n| Friendly\n| 4\n|-\n| align=center|50\n| 3 July\n| [[K\u00f8benhavns Idr\u00e6tspark|Idr\u00e6tsparken]], Copenhagen\n| {{fb|Denmark}}\n| align=center|2\u20130\n| Friendly\n| \n|-\n| align=center|51\n| 5 July\n| [[Silesian Stadium]], [[Chorz\u00f3w]]\n| {{fb|Poland}}\n| align=center|1\u20130\n| Friendly\n| \n|-\n| align=center|52\n| 11 July\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|Uruguay}}\n| align=center|0\u20130\n| [[1966 FIFA World Cup]]\n| \n|-\n| align=center|53\n| 16 July\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|Mexico|1934}}\n| align=center|2\u20130\n| [[1966 FIFA World Cup]]\n| \n|-\n| align=center|54\n| 20 July\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|France}}\n| align=center|2\u20130\n| [[1966 FIFA World Cup]]\n| \n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''1967'''\n|-\n| align=center|55\n| 15 April\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|Scotland}}\n| align=center|2\u20133\n| [[1966\u201367 British Home Championship]]\n| \n|-\n| align=center|56\n| 24 May\n| [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], London\n| {{fb|Spain|1945}}\n| align=center|2\u20130\n| Friendly\n| 1\n|-\n| align=center|57\n| 27 May\n| [[Ernst-Happel-Stadion|Praterstadion]], Vienna\n| {{fb|Austria}}\n| align=center|1\u20130\n| Friendly\n| \n|}\n\n==Honours==\n===Club===\n'''Chelsea'''\n*[[FA Youth Cup]] 