al's Songbird]]\" || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Analog Science Fact & Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo79\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Thomas|Disch}} || {{sort|\"Man Who Had No Idea\"|\"[[The Man Who Had No Idea]]\"}} || ''{{sort|Magazine of Fantasy & Science Fiction|[[The Magazine of Fantasy & Science Fiction]]}}''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo79\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Dean|Ing}} || \"[[Devil You Don't Know]]\" || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Analog Science Fact & Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo79\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|John|Varley|John Varley (author)}} || {{sort|\"Barbie Murders\"|\"[[Eight Worlds|The Barbie Murders]]\"}} || ''[[Asimov's Science Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo79\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"6\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"| [[1979 in literature|1980]]\n| {{sortname|George R. R.|Martin}}* || \"[[Sandkings (novelette)|Sandkings]]\" || ''[[Omni (magazine)|Omni]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo80\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Barry B.|Longyear}} || \"Homecoming\" || ''[[Asimov's Science Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo80\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Larry|Niven}} || {{sort|\"Locusts\"|\"The Locusts\"}} || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Analog Science Fact & Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo80\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Vonda N.|McIntyre}} || \"Fireflood\" || ''{{sort|Magazine of Fantasy & Science Fiction|[[The Magazine of Fantasy & Science Fiction]]}}''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo80\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|John|Varley|John Varley (author)}} || \"[[Eight Worlds|Options]]\" || ''{{sort|Universe 09|Universe #9}}'' ([[Bantam Spectra]])\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo80\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Christopher|Priest|Christopher Priest (novelist)}} || \"Palely Loitering\" || ''{{sort|Magazine of Fantasy & Science Fiction|[[The Magazine of Fantasy & Science Fiction]]}}''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo80\"/>\n