ccessdate=2010-04-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVFYMsr?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1991-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hugo92\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1992-hugo-awards/ |title=1992 Hugo Awards |publisher=World Science Fiction Society |accessdate=2010-04-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVFlG5L?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1992-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hugo93\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1993-hugo-awards/ |title=1993 Hugo Awards |publisher=World Science Fiction Society |accessdate=2010-04-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVFyAKQ?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1993-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hugo94\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1994-hugo-awards/ |title=1994 Hugo Awards |publisher=World Science Fiction Society |accessdate=2010-04-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVGBv5f?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1994-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hugo95\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1995-hugo-awards/ |title=1995 Hugo Awards |publisher=World Science Fiction Society |accessdate=2010-04-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVGP9s3?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1995-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hugo96\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1996-hugo-awards/ |title=1996 Hugo Awards |publisher=World Science Fiction Society |accessdate=2010-04-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVGbnTP?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1996-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hugo97\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.or