944]]\n!align=\"center\" rowspan=\"7\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"| 2019\n| {{sortname|C. L.|Moore}}* (as [[Lewis Padgett]])\n|rowspan=\"2\"| \"[[Mimsy Were the Borogoves]]\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Astounding Science-Fiction]]''\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo44\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| {{sortname|Henry|Kuttner}}* (as [[Lewis Padgett]])\n|-\n| {{sortname|Leigh|Brackett}} || \"Citadel of Lost Ships\" || ''[[Planet Stories]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo44\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Leigh|Brackett}} || {{sort|\"Halfling\"|\"The Halfling\"}} || ''[[Astonishing Stories]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo44\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Henry|Kuttner}} (as [[Lewis Padgett]]) || {{sort|\"Proud Robot\"|\"The Proud Robot\"}} || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Astounding Science-Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo44\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Eric Frank|Russell}} || \"Symbiotica\" || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Astounding Science-Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo44\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Fritz|Leiber}} || \"Thieves' House\" || ''[[Unknown (magazine)|Unknown Worlds]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo44\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"8\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"| [[1944 in literature|1945]]\n!align=\"center\" rowspan=\"8\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"| 2020\n| {{sortname|Fredric|Brown}} || \"Arena\" || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Astounding Science-Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo45\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Isaac|Asimov}} || {{sort|\"Big and the Little\"|\"[[Foundation (Asimov novel)|The Big and the Little]]\" (\"The Merchant Princes\")}} || ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|Astounding Science-Fiction]]''\n|align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Hugo45\"/>\n|-\n| {{sortname|C. L.|Moore}} (as Lawrence O'Donnell)\n|rowspan=\"2\"| {{sort|\"Children's Hour\"|\"The Children's Hour\"}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Analog Science Fiction and Fact|